93f02b1d138797561d14df697fe01afa56af454b6b8c0a5d317d6e62a2dd78d614bd64dfc57b5c16ef18ae42a4a7dadc64a2109ac87392feedc9373f682e05da  0001-spinner-Add-support-for-wayland-backend.patch
